2:T6c4,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you print custom Nepal flags and institutional sets?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We produce national and custom flags from approved geometry, including desk, ceremonial, and outdoor formats. Share finish size, quantity, and deadline so we can recommend fabric and finishing."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the typical turnaround for flag printing in Kathmandu?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Timing depends on proof approval, material availability, and queue. Simple runs often move quickly after artwork is locked; multi-piece ceremonial sets or large banners need more production time. Contact us with your date and we will confirm a realistic calendar."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you handle bulk orders for clubs, schools, or corporate campaigns?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We regularly support repeat buyers and campaign-scale work. Quantities, packaging, and delivery across Nepal’s provinces can be planned in the brief so production stays predictable."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you offer gold and silver foil, banners, and jersey printing in one studio?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Our capability map covers foil, paper, jersey customization, and advertisement banners in addition to flags. One brief can combine formats when timelines align."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I get an accurate quote?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Use the contact form or WhatsApp with dimensions, quantity, usage (indoor/outdoor/ceremony), and any logo or colour references. We respond with material options and next steps."}}]}a:Ta70,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https://flagsnepal.com/#organization","name":"Flags Nepal","url":"https://flagsnepal.com","logo":"https://flagsnepal.com/flags-nepal-logo-site.png","image":["https://flagsnepal.com/f